WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:05.690 size:75%
We live in a world defined by time, space, and distance.

00:00:05.690 --> 00:00:09.919 size:75%
A safe environment where we all live together should be within our reach.

00:00:09.919 --> 00:00:13.339 size:75%
Today, thanks to a major collaborative effort between

00:00:13.339 --> 00:00:17.980 size:75%
business leaders, medical professionals, engineers, and scientists,

00:00:17.980 --> 00:00:24.359 size:75%
there is a new, accurate, and inexpensive way to ensure a safe space in your daily activities,

00:00:24.359 --> 00:00:26.480 size:40%
on your mobile device.

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:29.779 size:80%
SafeSphere is the first technology using mobile devices

00:00:29.779 --> 00:00:32.470 size:60%
to identify how close we are to each other

00:00:32.470 --> 00:00:37.280 size:85%
reducing risk and exposure to businesses and their customers.

00:00:37.280 --> 00:00:41.830 size:90%
Using precise acoustic signals, SafeSphere's proprietary technology

00:00:41.830 --> 00:00:44.800 size:65%
accurately determines your proximity to others

00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:48.890 size:70%
and alerts you to keep the safe distance you define.

00:00:48.890 --> 00:00:52.120 size:80%
SafeSphere easily integrates with existing mobile apps,

00:00:52.120 --> 00:00:54.010 size:50%
to help create a safer environment

00:00:54.010 --> 00:00:57.740 size:80%
with minimal costs and physical changes to your facilities.

00:00:57.740 --> 00:01:01.900 size:70%
SafeSphere was designed from the ground up to help keep everyone safe:

00:01:01.900 --> 00:01:02.740 size:25%
employees,

00:01:02.740 --> 00:01:04.199 size:25%
customers,

00:01:04.199 --> 00:01:05.300 size:25%
students,

00:01:05.300 --> 00:01:06.600 size:25%
patients,

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:09.010 size:50%
as well as families and friends.

00:01:09.010 --> 00:01:13.800 size:70%
SafeSphere lets smartphones monitor distance between users to keep us safer when:

00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:14.500 size:25%
studying,

00:01:14.500 --> 00:01:15.800 size:25%
working,

00:01:15.800 --> 00:01:16.880 size:25%
dining,

00:01:16.880 --> 00:01:18.000 size:25%
shopping,

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:18.900 size:25%
traveling,

00:01:18.900 --> 00:01:20.200 size:25%
playing,

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:21.500 size:25%
staying active,

00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:24.000 size:35%
enjoying the outdoors.

00:01:25.300 --> 00:01:27.700 size:55%
SafeSphere brings the world closer

00:01:27.700 --> 00:01:29.540 size:35%
but not too close.

